msgstr "从最近的文章中提取轻量级的站点范围或特定于作者的写作风格基线。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1200
msgid "Build Article Production Fingerprint"
msgstr "构建文章生产指纹"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1201
msgid ""
"Builds a stable lightweight production fingerprint for article dedupe and "
"result summaries."
msgstr "为文章重复数据删除和结果摘要构建稳定的轻量级生产指纹。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1244
msgid "Check Article Production Duplicate"
msgstr "检查文章制作重复"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1245
msgid ""
"Checks whether a lightweight article production fingerprint already exists "
"on a post."
msgstr "检查文章上是否已存在轻量级文章生产指纹。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1272
msgid "Review Article Output Light"
msgstr "评论文章 输出光"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1273
msgid ""
"Builds lightweight local article quality, style, image, and AI-risk review "
"signals without model calls."
msgstr "无需模型调用即可构建轻量级本地文章质量、风格、图像和 AI 风险审核信号。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1310
msgid "Compose Article Production Result"
msgstr "撰写文章 制作结果"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1311
msgid ""
"Summarizes the article production mainline with result mode, degraded "
"reasons, fingerprint, handoff, and next action."
msgstr "总结文章生成主线，包括结果模式、降级原因、指纹、切换和下一步操作。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1346
msgid "Compose Article Draft Result"
msgstr "撰写文章草稿结果"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1347
msgid ""
"Composes one canonical draft workflow result with draft content, metadata "
"resolution, shared SEO/GEO review, and handoff hints."
msgstr ""
"使用草稿内容、元数据解析、共享的 SEO/GEO 审核和移交提示组成一份规范的草稿工作"
"流程结果。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1383
msgid "Resolve Article Publication Decision"
msgstr "解决文章发表决定"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1384
msgid ""
"Resolves a deterministic article publish, schedule, review, or draft handoff "
"after quality and duplicate checks."
msgstr "解决质量和重复检查后的确定性文章发布、计划、审阅或草稿移交问题。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1422
msgid "Build Article Style Profile"
msgstr "建立文章风格档案"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1423
msgid ""
"Merges baseline, reference, and explicit writing-style hints into one "
"lightweight article style profile."
msgstr "将基线、参考和明确的写作风格提示合并到一个轻量级的文章风格配置文件中。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1459
msgid "Route Content Intent"
msgstr "路由内容意图"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1460
msgid ""
"Normalizes a natural-language content request to one supported Gutenberg "
"recipe route without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "将自然语言内容请求规范化为一个受支持的 Gutenberg 配方路由，而不写入 WordPress 内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1504
msgid "Evaluate Gutenberg Recipe Suite"
msgstr "评估 Gutenberg 配方套件"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1505
msgid ""
"Runs read-only natural-language routing and Gutenberg plan quality gates "
"across a batch of recipe prompts."
msgstr "对一批配方提示运行只读自然语言路由和 Gutenberg 计划质量门禁。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1567
msgid "Get Gutenberg Block Capability Catalog"
msgstr "获取 Gutenberg 区块能力目录"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1568
msgid ""
"Returns bounded Gutenberg-native block composition rules for AI planners "
"without creating proposals or writing content."
msgstr "向 AI 规划器返回有边界的 Gutenberg 原生区块组合规则，而不创建提案或写入内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1602
msgid "Compose Gutenberg Block Plan"
msgstr "组合 Gutenberg 区块计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1603
msgid ""
"Routes a natural-language Gutenberg request, builds a read-only plan, "
"reviews it, and applies one bounded repair pass before Core proposal handoff."
msgstr "路由自然语言 Gutenberg 请求，构建只读计划，审核该计划，并在移交 Core 提案前执行一次有边界的修复。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1653
msgid "Inspect Gutenberg Composition Contract"
msgstr "检查 Gutenberg 组合合约"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1654
msgid ""
"Inspects one post, page, Site Editor template, template part, or proposed "
"block tree against the bounded Gutenberg composition contract without "
"scanning the full site or writing content."
msgstr "根据有边界的 Gutenberg 组合合约检查一篇文章、一个页面、站点编辑器模板、模板部件或拟议区块树，而不扫描整站或写入内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1706
msgid "Build Article Block Plan"
msgstr "构建文章区块计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1707
msgid ""
"Builds a governed draft post plan from whitelisted Gutenberg-native "
"editorial article blocks without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "基于白名单内的 Gutenberg 原生编辑文章区块构建受治理的文章草稿计划，而不写入 WordPress 内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1748
msgid "Get Block Theme Context"
msgstr "获取区块主题上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1749
msgid ""
"Returns compact active block theme Site Editor context for governed OpenClaw "
"planning."
msgstr "为受治理的 OpenClaw 规划返回紧凑的当前区块主题站点编辑器上下文。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1771
msgid "Get Template Blocks"
msgstr "获取模板区块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1772
msgid ""
"Returns parsed blocks from one wp_template entity for review and "
"verification."
msgstr "返回一个 wp_template 实体中解析后的区块，用于审核和验证。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1794
msgid "Get Template Part Blocks"
msgstr "获取模板部件区块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1795
msgid ""
"Returns parsed blocks from one wp_template_part entity for review and "
"verification."
msgstr "返回一个 wp_template_part 实体中解析后的区块，用于审核和验证。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1817
msgid "Inspect Block Theme Surface"
msgstr "检查区块主题表面"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1818
msgid ""
"Inspects supported block theme template issues and returns stable issue "
"codes before any governed Site Editor plan is built."
msgstr "在构建任何受治理的站点编辑器计划前，检查受支持的区块主题模板问题并返回稳定的问题代码。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1856
msgid "Build Block Theme Site Plan"
msgstr "构建区块主题站点计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1857
msgid ""
"Builds a governed block theme site configuration plan without writing "
"WordPress Site Editor entities."
msgstr "构建受治理的区块主题站点配置计划，而不写入 WordPress 站点编辑器实体。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1907
msgid "Build Pattern Page Plan"
msgstr "构建页面样板计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1908
msgid ""
"Builds a governed page draft plan from a whitelisted Gutenberg page pattern "
"without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "基于白名单内的 Gutenberg 页面样板构建受治理的页面草稿计划，而不写入 WordPress 内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1971
msgid "Review Pattern Page"
msgstr "审核页面样板"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1972
msgid ""
"Reviews a Gutenberg pattern page or proposed block tree for layout, media, "
"responsive, and editor-risk signals without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "审核 Gutenberg 页面样板或拟议区块树的布局、媒体、响应式和编辑器风险信号，而不写入 WordPress 内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2010
msgid "Review Block Editor Surface"
msgstr "审核区块编辑器表面"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2011
msgid ""
"Reviews a post, page, Site Editor template, template part, or proposed block "
"tree for block-editor quality signals without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "审核文章、页面、站点编辑器模板、模板部件或拟议区块树的区块编辑器质量信号，而不写入 WordPress 内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2058
msgid "List Pages"
msgstr "列表页"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2059
msgid ""
"Lists WordPress pages with status, parent, search, sorting, and pagination "
"filters."
msgstr "列出带有状态、父级、搜索、排序和分页过滤器的 WordPress 页面。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2091
msgid "Get Page"
msgstr "获取页面"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2092
msgid ""
"Returns a single WordPress page, including content, template, hierarchy, "
"author, and optional meta."
msgstr "返回单个 WordPress 页面，包括内容、模板、层次结构、作者和可选元。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2138
msgid "Inspect Page Structure"
msgstr "检查页面结构"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2139
msgid ""
"Inspects WordPress page hierarchy, template usage, and orphaned parent "
"relationships without modifying pages."
msgstr ""
"在不修改页面的情况下检查 WordPress 页面层次结构、模板使用情况和孤立父关系。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2168
msgid "List Pages Tree"
msgstr "列表页面树"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2169
msgid ""
"Returns a hierarchical page tree for navigation and site-structure review."
msgstr "返回用于导航和站点结构审查的分层页面树。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2209
msgid "Get Content Publishing Checklist"
msgstr "获取内容发布清单"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2210
msgid ""
"Returns a deterministic pre-publish readiness checklist for one post or page "
"without applying changes."
msgstr "返回一篇文章或页面的确定性预发布准备清单，而不应用更改。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2254
msgid "Get Content Inventory Health"
msgstr "获取内容库存健康状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2255
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded content inventory and summarizes missing titles, thin "
"content, excerpt gaps, media gaps, SEO metadata gaps, and stale content."
msgstr ""
"扫描有限的内容清单并总结缺失的标题、薄弱的内容、摘录差距、媒体差距、SEO 元数"
"据差距和过时的内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2300
msgid "Get Nonproduction Content Inventory"
msgstr "获取非生产内容清单"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2301
msgid ""
"Detects bounded smoke, fixture, and nonproduction content that may distort "
"content, taxonomy, comment, and operations diagnostics without mutating the "
"site."
msgstr ""
"检测可能扭曲内容、分类、评论和操作诊断而不改变站点的有限烟雾、固定装置和非生"
"产内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2334
msgid "Build Nonproduction Content Cleanup Plan"
msgstr "制定非生产内容清理计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2335
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only cleanup plan for detected nonproduction content, mapping "
"each candidate to existing governed write abilities without trashing or "
"deleting anything."
msgstr ""
"为检测到的非生产内容构建只读清理计划，将每个候选内容映射到现有的受控写入能"
"力，不移入回收站，也不删除任何内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2369
msgid "Build Content Inventory Fix Plan"
msgstr "制定内容库存修复计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2370
msgid ""
"Maps bounded content inventory issues to reviewable fix actions that reuse "
"existing governed write abilities without mutating posts."
msgstr ""
"将有限的内容库存问题映射到可审查的修复操作，这些修复操作可重用现有的受控写入"
"功能，而无需更改文章。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2404
msgid "Get Bulk Publishing Checklist"
msgstr "获取批量发布清单"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2405
msgid ""
"Runs the read-only publishing checklist for a bounded list of posts and "
"returns batch readiness totals."
msgstr "运行有限的文章列表的只读发布清单并返回批次准备情况总计。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2451
msgid "Get Internal Link Opportunity Report"
msgstr "获取内部链接机会报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2452
msgid ""
"Builds a post-id based internal-link opportunity report with candidate "
"targets, anchor suggestions, and placement hints."
msgstr ""
"构建基于文章 ID 的内部链接机会报告，其中包含候选目标、锚点建议和放置提示。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2492
msgid "Get Site Operations Dashboard"
msgstr "获取站点操作仪表板"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2493
msgid ""
"Builds a bounded read-only site operations dashboard for content status, "
"inventory issues, taxonomy health, comments, and media signals."
msgstr ""
"为内容状态、库存问题、分类健康状况、评论和媒体信号构建有界只读站点操作仪表"
"板。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2522
msgid "Get Post Publish Risk Report"
msgstr "获取发布后风险报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2523
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only publish risk report for one post from checklist, SEO/GEO, "
"revision, and internal-link signals."
msgstr "根据清单、SEO/GEO、修订和内部链接信号为一篇文章构建只读发布风险报告。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2553
msgid "Get Article Publish Preflight Context"
msgstr "获取文章 发布 预检上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2554
msgid ""
"Aggregates post context, publishing checklist, publish risk, workflow "
"context, and calendar context for host-side publish preflight workflows "
"without writing."
msgstr ""
"聚合发布上下文、发布清单、发布风险、工作流上下文和日历上下文，以供 host 端发"
"布预检工作流而不写入。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2586
msgid "Get Content Refresh Opportunities"
msgstr "获得内容刷新机会"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2587
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded content set and returns stale, thin, SEO-light, answer-"
"light, and low-link refresh opportunities."
msgstr ""
"扫描有界内容集并返回陈旧、稀疏、SEO-light、answer-light 和低链接刷新机会。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2619
msgid "Get Old Article Refresh Context"
msgstr "获取旧文章刷新上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2620
msgid ""
"Aggregates refresh opportunities, SEO/GEO gaps, site style baseline, "
"internal-link graph health, and optional selected-post link opportunities "
"for host-side old article refresh workflows."
msgstr ""
"聚合 host 端旧文章刷新工作流程的刷新机会、SEO/GEO 差距、网站样式基线、内部链"
"接图运行状况以及可选的选定文章链接机会。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2654
msgid "Get Internal Link Graph Health"
msgstr "获取内部链接图健康状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2655
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded content set and summarizes outgoing links, incoming links, "
"orphan posts, and candidate internal-link pairs."
msgstr "扫描有界内容集并总结传出链接、传入链接、孤立文章和候选内部链接对。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2687
msgid "Get Media Cleanup Opportunities"
msgstr "获得媒体清理机会"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2688
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded media inventory and returns cleanup opportunities for "
"metadata gaps, source gaps, and likely unused assets."
msgstr ""
"扫描有限的媒体库存并返回元数据间隙、源间隙和可能未使用的资产的清理机会。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2717
msgid "List Media Backups"
msgstr "列出媒体备份"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2718
msgid ""
"Lists recorded backup files for one attachment media operation history "
"without mutating media."
msgstr "列出一份附件媒体操作历史记录的备份文件，无需更改媒体。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2747
msgid "Build Media Inventory Fix Plan"
msgstr "制定媒体库存修复计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2748
msgid ""
"Maps bounded media inventory issues to reviewable metadata and cleanup "
"actions that reuse existing governed write abilities without mutating media."
msgstr ""
"将有限的媒体库存问题映射到可审查的元数据和清理操作，以重用现有的受控写入功能"
"而不改变媒体。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2787
msgid "Build Media Reference Repair Plan"
msgstr "构建介质参考修复计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2788
msgid ""
"Scans post content for hard-coded URLs to a previously replaced media file "
"and builds governed patch-post-content actions without mutating posts."
msgstr ""
"扫描文章内容以查找之前替换的媒体文件中的硬编码 URL，并构建受管理的补丁文章内"
"容操作，而无需更改文章。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2823
msgid "Build Media Adoption Enhancement Plan"
msgstr "构建媒体采用增强计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2824
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only batch plan that imports a reviewed remote image, "
"generates an optimized derivative, and optionally patches one post from an "
"old media URL to the optimized derivative."
msgstr ""
"构建只读批处理计划：导入已审核的远程图片，"
"生成优化衍生文件，"
"并可选地将一篇文章中的旧媒体 URL 修补为优化衍生文件 URL。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2871
msgid "Build Image Candidate Adoption Plan"
msgstr "构建图片候选采用计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2872
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only batch plan for importing one reviewed image candidate, "
"applying reviewed media metadata, and optionally setting it as a post "
"featured image."
msgstr ""
"构建只读批处理计划：导入一个已审核的图片候选，"
"应用已审核的媒体元数据，"
"并可选地将其设为文章特色图片。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2920
msgid "Build Image Candidate Review Artifact"
msgstr "构建图片候选审核工件"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2921
msgid ""
"Normalizes already retrieved image_candidate.v1 rows into a review-only "
"artifact and lightweight recommendation projections without searching, "
"generating, importing, or writing media."
msgstr ""
"将已获取的 image_candidate.v1 行规范化为仅供审核的工件和轻量推荐投影，"
"不搜索、不生成、不导入，也不写入媒体。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2955
msgid "Build Media Settings Reference Repair Plan"
msgstr "构建媒体设置参考修复计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2956
msgid ""
"Scans selected WordPress options and theme mods for hard-coded URLs to a "
"previously replaced media file and builds governed exact replacement actions "
"without mutating settings."
msgstr ""
"扫描选定的 WordPress 选项和主题模组以将 URL 硬编码到之前替换的媒体文件中，并"
"构建受管控的精确替换操作，而无需更改设置。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:2999
msgid "Get Taxonomy Consolidation Suggestions"
msgstr "获取分类整合建议"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3000
msgid ""
"Scans taxonomy terms and suggests read-only consolidation candidates for "
"empty, duplicate, similar, and unused terms."
msgstr "扫描分类项并针对空的、重复的、相似的和未使用的术语建议只读合并候选。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3030
msgid "Suggest Post Taxonomy Terms"
msgstr "建议文章分类项"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3031
msgid ""
"Ranks existing category and tag candidates against a supplied post context "
"without creating terms or mutating posts."
msgstr ""
"根据提供的文章上下文对现有分类和标签候选进行排序，"
"不创建分类项，也不更改文章。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3108
msgid "Propose Post Taxonomy Terms"
msgstr "提出后分类项"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3109
msgid ""
"Builds a deterministic post taxonomy assignment proposal from existing terms "
"without mutating the post or creating terms."
msgstr "根据现有术语构建确定性的文章分类分配提案，而无需更改文章或创建术语。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3153
msgid "Get Page Structure Health"
msgstr "获取页面结构健康状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3154
msgid ""
"Scans one page or a bounded page set and reports heading, CTA, content "
"depth, and block structure health."
msgstr "扫描一页或有界页面集并报告标题、{{​​CTA}}、内容深度和块结构运行状况。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3183
msgid "Get SEO GEO Gap Report"
msgstr "获取 SEO GEO 差距报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3184
msgid ""
"Builds a bounded SEO/GEO gap report from topic coverage, refresh "
"opportunities, answer structure, and SEO metadata signals."
msgstr ""
"根据主题覆盖范围、刷新机会、答案结构和 SEO 元数据信号构建有界 SEO/GEO 差距报"
"告。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3215
msgid "Get Site Style Baseline"
msgstr "获取网站风格基线"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3216
msgid ""
"Returns a compact read-only site-wide or author-specific writing style "
"baseline from recent posts."
msgstr "从最近的文章中返回紧凑的只读站点范围或特定于作者的写作风格基线。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3245
msgid "Build Article Workflow Context"
msgstr "构建文章工作流程上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3246
msgid ""
"Builds one read-only context bundle for article refresh, publish, or new-"
"article workflows without model routing."
msgstr ""
"为文章刷新、发布或新文章工作流程构建一个只读上下文捆绑包，无需模型路由。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3275
msgid "Get Publishing Calendar Context"
msgstr "获取发布日历上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3276
msgid ""
"Returns scheduled posts, draft backlog, pending review items, and near-term "
"publishing cadence context."
msgstr "返回计划的文章、待办事项草稿、待审核项目和近期发布节奏上下文。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3305
msgid "Get Media Inventory Health"
msgstr "获取媒体库存状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3306
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded media inventory and summarizes missing alt text, captions, "
"descriptions, source metadata, and format attention."
msgstr ""
"扫描有限的媒体清单并总结丢失的替代文本、标题、描述、源元数据和格式注意。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3349
msgid "Inspect Media Asset"
msgstr "检查媒体资产"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3350
msgid ""
"Inspects one attachment file and returns read-only format, size, dimension, "
"and optimization recommendations."
msgstr "检查一个附件文件并返回只读格式、大小、维度和优化建议。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3402
msgid "Build Media Derivative Cloud Request"
msgstr "构建媒体衍生云请求"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3403
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only request contract for a host or Cloud addon to generate an "
"optimized media derivative without uploading, calling Cloud, or mutating "
"WordPress."
msgstr ""
"为主机或 Cloud Addon 构建只读请求合约，以生成优化的媒体衍生品，而无需上传、调"
"用云或更改 WordPress。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3472
msgid "Build Media Optimization Plan"
msgstr "制定媒体优化计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3473
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only one-attachment optimization plan that combines reviewed "
"media metadata updates with a governed derivative adoption action for one "
"Core approval."
msgstr ""
"构建一项只读单附件优化计划，该计划将经过审核的媒体元数据更新与受管理的派生采"
"用操作相结合，以获得一次 Core 批准。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3507
msgid "Build Media Adoption Preflight Summary"
msgstr "构建媒体采用预检摘要"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3508
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only preflight summary for adopting one reviewed media "
"derivative artifact, including current asset evidence, derivative "
"comparison, bounded content-reference impact, and next-step guidance without "
"mutating WordPress."
msgstr ""
"为采用一个已审核的媒体衍生工件构建只读预检摘要，"
"包括当前资产证据、衍生文件对比、"
"有边界的内容引用影响和下一步指引，而不更改 WordPress。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3557
msgid "Build Media Rename Plan"
msgstr "构建媒体重命名计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3558
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only one-attachment rename plan for a reviewed target media "
"file name and exact post-content reference updates without mutating "
"WordPress."
msgstr ""
"为已审核的目标媒体文件名和准确的内容后参考更新构建只读单附件重命名计划，而无"
"需更改 WordPress。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3595
msgid "Build Media Derivative Batch Plan"
msgstr "构建媒体衍生批次计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3596
msgid ""
"Builds a bounded read-only plan for batch Cloud media derivative previews "
"from local media filters without calling Cloud, creating proposals, or "
"mutating WordPress."
msgstr ""
"为从本地媒体过滤器批量云媒体衍生品预览构建有界只读计划，无需调用云、创建提案"
"或改变 WordPress。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3693
msgid "Get Post SEO GEO Readiness"
msgstr "准备好发布 SEO GEO"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3694
msgid ""
"Returns one deterministic SEO/GEO readiness snapshot for a post, including "
"metadata, content-depth, question, and media signals."
msgstr ""
"返回文章的一个确定性 SEO/GEO 准备情况快照，包括元数据、内容深度、问题和媒体信"
"号。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3735
msgid "Get Site Topic Coverage Report"
msgstr "获取网站主题覆盖率报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3736
msgid ""
"Builds a bounded site topic coverage summary from post titles, terms, and "
"content snippets without model routing."
msgstr "从文章标题、术语和内容片段构建有界站点主题覆盖摘要，无需模型路由。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3778
msgid "Get Taxonomy Inventory Health"
msgstr "获取分类库存健康状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3779
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded taxonomy term inventory and summarizes empty, unused, "
"duplicate, and hierarchy attention signals."
msgstr "扫描有界分类项清单并总结空的、未使用的、重复的和层次结构注意信号。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3823
msgid "Get Revision Change Risk Report"
msgstr "获取修订变更风险报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3824
msgid ""
"Reads recent revisions for one post and summarizes title, content length, "
"block count, and recency change-risk signals."
msgstr "阅读一篇文章的最新修订并总结标题、内容长度、块计数和新近变化风险信号。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:3906
msgid "Workflow recipe definition was not found."
msgstr "未找到工作流程配方定义。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:4180
#: includes/Packages/Read_Traits/Content_Inventory_Read_Methods.php:35
#: includes/Packages/Read_Traits/Post_Primitives_Read_Methods.php:44
#: includes/Packages/Read_Traits/Post_Primitives_Read_Methods.php:281
#: includes/Packages/Read_Traits/Post_Primitives_Read_Methods.php:393
msgid "Post type does not exist."
msgstr "文章类型不存在。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:4208
msgid "Content is required to generate an excerpt proposal."
msgstr "生成摘要提案需要内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:4223
msgid "Local read-only excerpt proposal generated from explicit content input."
msgstr "从显式内容输入生成的本地只读摘录提案。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:4283
msgid "Post metadata plan resolved."
msgstr "发布元数据计划已解决。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:4435
msgid "Menu was not found."
msgstr "找不到菜单。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:72
msgid ""
"Host-governed WordPress write abilities with dry-run previews and external "
"approval."
msgstr "host 治理的 WordPress 写入功能，具有 dry-run 预览和外部批准。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:103
msgid "Create Draft"
msgstr "创建草稿"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:104
msgid ""
"Creates a draft post or page after host approval, or returns a dry-run "
"preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后创建草稿文章或页面，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:150
msgid "Update Post"
msgstr "更新文章"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:151
msgid ""
"Updates a post title, content, or excerpt after host approval, or returns a "
"dry-run preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后更新文章标题、内容或摘录，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:184
msgid "Set Post SEO Meta"
msgstr "设置文章 SEO 元"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:185
msgid ""
"Updates SEO title and description metadata for one post after host approval, "
"or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后更新一篇文章的 SEO 标题和描述元数据，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:216
msgid "Patch Post Content"
msgstr "补丁发布内容"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:217
msgid ""
"Applies text patch operations to saved post content after host approval, or "
"returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后将文本修补操作应用于保存的文章内容，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:267
msgid "Patch Setting Value"
msgstr "补丁设置值"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:268
msgid ""
"Applies exact text replacement operations to one option or theme mod after "
"host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后将精确的文本替换操作应用于一个选项或主题模组，或默认返回 dry-"
"run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:320
msgid "Update Post Blocks"
msgstr "更新文章块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:321
msgid ""
"Writes Gutenberg blocks into post content after host approval, or returns a "
"dry-run preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后将 Gutenberg 块写入文章内容，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:361
msgid "Update Template Blocks"
msgstr "更新模板区块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:362
msgid ""
"Writes reviewed Gutenberg blocks into a wp_template entity after host "
"approval, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后将已审核的 Gutenberg 区块写入 wp_template 实体，"
"或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:405
msgid "Upsert Template Blocks"
msgstr "创建或更新模板区块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:406
msgid ""
"Creates or updates a reviewed wp_template override after host approval, or "
"returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后创建或更新已审核的 wp_template 覆盖项，"
"或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:456
msgid "Update Template Part Blocks"
msgstr "更新模板部件区块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:457
msgid ""
"Writes reviewed Gutenberg blocks into a wp_template_part entity after host "
"approval, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后将已审核的 Gutenberg 区块写入 wp_template_part 实体，"
"或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:500
msgid "Set Post Slug"
msgstr "设置柱塞"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:501
msgid ""
"Updates a post slug after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后更新文章，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:529
msgid "Set Post Author"
msgstr "设置文章作者"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:530
msgid ""
"Updates a post author after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后更新文章作者，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:557
msgid "Set Post Template"
msgstr "设置文章模板"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:558
msgid ""
"Updates a post template after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后更新文章模板，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:585
msgid "Set Post Format"
msgstr "设置文章格式"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:586
msgid ""
"Updates a post format after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后更新文章格式，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:616
msgid "Create Term"
msgstr "创建术语"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:617
msgid ""
"Creates a taxonomy term after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后创建分类项，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:647
msgid "Update Term"
msgstr "更新期限"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:648
msgid ""
"Updates a taxonomy term after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后更新分类项，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:682
msgid "Set Post Terms"
msgstr "设置文章条款"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:683
msgid ""
"Updates a post taxonomy terms in replace, append, or remove mode after host "
"approval, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后以替换、追加或删除模式更新文章分类项，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:733
msgid "Update Media Details"
msgstr "更新媒体详细信息"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:734
msgid ""
"Updates attachment title, alt, caption, description, and attribution fields "
"after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后更新附件标题、替代项、标题、描述和属性字段，或默认返回 dry-run "
"预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:780
msgid "Upload Media From URL"
msgstr "从 URL 上传媒体"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:781
msgid ""
"Downloads one remote media asset into the WordPress media library after host "
"approval, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后将一项远程媒体资源下载到 WordPress 媒体库中，或默认返回 dry-"
"run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:828
msgid "Optimize Media Asset"
msgstr "优化媒体资产"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:829
msgid ""
"Generates an optimized derivative for one image attachment after host "
"approval, preserving the original file."
msgstr "在 host 批准后为一个图像附件生成优化的衍生文件，并保留原始文件。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:865
msgid "Replace Media File"
msgstr "替换媒体文件"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:866
msgid ""
"Replaces one attachment main file with a previously generated optimized "
"derivative after host approval, preserving backup metadata for restore-media-"
"backup."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后，将一个附件主文件替换为先前生成的优化衍生文件，并保留用于恢复"
"媒体备份的备份元数据。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:906
msgid "Restore Media Backup"
msgstr "恢复媒体备份"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:907
msgid ""
"Restores one attachment by copying a recorded backup back to the original "
"media path and URL after host approval."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后，通过将录制的备份复制回原始媒体路径和 URL 来恢复一个附件。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:947
msgid "Rename Media File"
msgstr "重命名媒体文件"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:948
msgid ""
"Renames one attachment main file within its current uploads directory after "
"host approval, preserving a backup and rollback metadata."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后重命名当前上传目录中的一个附件主文件，保留备份和回滚元数据。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:986
msgid "Adopt Cloud Media Derivative"
msgstr "采用云媒体衍生品"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:987
msgid ""
"Adopts one approved short-lived Cloud derivative artifact as the attachment "
"main file, with local backup and rollback metadata."
msgstr ""
"采用一个经批准的短期云衍生工件作为附件主文件，并具有本地备份和回滚元数据。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1032
msgid "Set Post Featured Image"
msgstr "设置文章特色图片"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1033
msgid ""
"Sets a post featured image from an attachment ID or approved remote media "
"URL, or returns a dry-run preview by default."
msgstr ""
"设置来自附件 ID 或批准的远程媒体 URL 的文章特色图像，或默认返回 dry-run 预"
"览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1063
msgid "Schedule Post"
msgstr "安排文章"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1064
msgid ""
"Schedules a post for future publication after host approval, or returns a "
"dry-run preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后安排文章以便将来发布，或者默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1097
msgid "Publish Post"
msgstr "发布文章"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1098
msgid ""
"Publishes a draft or pending post after host approval. Only treat the post "
"as publicly accessible after this succeeds."
msgstr ""
"在 host 批准后发布草稿或待处理的文章。仅在成功后才将文章视为可公开访问。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1124
msgid "Restore Post"
msgstr "恢复文章"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1125
msgid ""
"Restores a trashed post or page after host approval, or returns a dry-run "
"preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后恢复已删除的文章或页面，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1150
msgid "Approve Comment"
msgstr "批准评论"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1151
msgid ""
"Approves one comment after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后批准一条评论，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1176
msgid "Reply Comment"
msgstr "回复评论"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:1177
msgid ""
"Replies to one comment as the current user after host approval, or returns a "
"dry-run preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 批准后以当前用户身份回复一条评论，或默认返回 dry-run 预览。"

